  "instructions": [
    "heat lard or oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "add garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add smoked paprika, cumin, and chili powder, cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add petit pois and cook, stirring occasionally, until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "season with salt to taste.",
    "warm tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "assemble tacos by spooning peas onto tortillas, topping with queso fresco or feta, and garnishing with cilantro.",
    "squeeze lemon juice over peas before serving."
